{{Han compound|金|t1=metal|㕣|ls=psc|c1=s|c2=p}} – a kind of metal.

===Etymology===
Most varieties have a pronunciation derived from a velar initial.
* {{zh-ref|Schuessler (2007)}} see it a re-etymologization towards {{ltc-l|掔|solid; hard}}.
* Per {{zh-ref|Liu (2022)}}, it is from {{bor|cmn|wuu|-}}, in which the character {{m|zh||鉛}} is used to denote an etymon meaning "tinplate" with this velar pronunciation. As for further etymology, Liu suggested it an Indo-European-sourced borrowing, cf. {{m+|w=y|en|can|t=metal container}}.

